queries.sql: SELECT `vr`.`visitor_name`, `vr`.`group_code`, `vr`.`v_code`, `vrh`.`department`, `vrh`.`company`, `sgl`.`check_in_time`, `sgl`.`check_out_time`, `vr`.`spendTime`, CASE WHEN sgl.check_out_time IS NULL THEN 'IN' ELSE 'OUT' END AS visit_status FROM `visitors` `vr` LEFT JOIN `visitor_request_header` `vrh` ON `vrh`.`id` = `vr`.`request_header_id` LEFT JOIN `security_gate_logs` `sgl` ON `vr`.`id` = `sgl`.`visitor_request_id` ORDER BY `sgl`.`check_in_time` DESC
